    "908908f3-2ca2-4385-a271-e5e3a437ef39": {
      "type": "faq-section",
      "blocks": {
        "bc576db1-ab1d-460a-ab68-d1c03cbbb4c6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-question": "How many uses will I get out of a bottle?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Each eco-concentrate dilutes to 300ml of Counter Clean. We recommend using one eco-concentrate per month. The Starter Kit is designed to last you 3 months. <br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "c8521687-4627-464d-8ccc-dba23e3635a3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-question": "Is this more expensive than a regular cleaner?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Counter Clean will cost you around 16p per day which is 3p more than a typical bottle of supermarket cleaner. However, we replace up to 16 different products under your sink so end up saving you money. <br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "b144c367-d9af-4fee-8901-3e2a634ef272": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-question": "How can I be sure it works?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Our product has been independently tested and proven to be 100% effective at tackling grease, grim and dirt. What’s more,. 93% of our 100k customers would recommend us for our cleaning power. </p>"
          }
        },
        "d1c26423-e811-47f7-9f5a-4d76284eaf65": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-question": "Is it safe around pets?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Our products are safe to use around dogs and other pets, however, it’s best not to use them to clean beds or food bowls without rinsing afterwards. If you are worried about allergies, do contact your vet. </p>"
          }
        },
        "b9c5f551-3e72-4565-8e96-69928933cfed": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq-question": "Is it Cruelty Free?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Yes, Counter Clean has never been tested on animals. We also only work with suppliers who also avoid testing on animals too!</p>"
          }
        },
        "021c4534-3673-4703-8b5a-783e243a7746": {
          "type": "text",
